resolution: "Shipped describeExtensionBlueprint in src/sdk/compose.ts, parity-locked to describeExtensionActivation."
expected_result: "An author-time, no-activation helper returns the same ExtensionActivationSummary as the runtime describe."
actual_result: "describeExtensionBlueprint added, barrel + /sdk/testing exported, deepEqual parity test green, 100% coverage."
